{"tid":2167378,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"德國擬立法規管狗主 每日必須帶狗散步兩次至少一小時","createTime":"2020-08-21T05:32:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T05:45:32.000Z","uid":1886,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e4e2efb9fd65f34ec7bcc032870afe3488139f9b","tid":2167378,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:32:26.000Z","msg":"德國宣佈正研究改革動物法，立法保障狗隻權益，包括每天必須有兩次散步機會，至少外出一小時等，最快明年初正式通過生效。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20200820/T3PT7NUJARGUJCBBADC4T3N2JM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20200820%2FT3PT7NUJARGUJCBBADC4T3N2JM%2F&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliu7O6ciNacqKxYXGqE8pVUEM%3D&h=1a283380\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20200820%2FT3PT7NUJARGUJCBBADC4T3N2JM%2F&h=9540d91c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20200820/T3PT7NUJARGUJCBBADC4T3N2JM/</a>"},{"pid":"963c931889ae9263e5c5b6cb401f2f26664a4166","tid":2167378,"uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:32:40.000Z","msg":"據外媒報道，德國農業部正部署改革動物法案，規管狗主。包括立法規定每日須帶狗散步兩次至少一小時，禁止長時間栓禁狗隻，不容許全日獨留狗隻在家等等。同時嚴厲打擊繁殖場，禁止繁殖者一次照顧三窩以上幼犬，並規定每天必須有人至少陪伴幼犬四小時，以確保小狗有足夠的社交。"},{"pid":"f51fcb6f3d615bedb1f14ed2fec68569fb090d9c","tid":2167378,"uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:32:51.000Z","msg":"就有關改革，德國農業部長Julia Kl&ouml;ckner明確表示「寵物並不是可愛的玩具，必須考慮到牠們的需求」，她亦強調法例是基於動物專家的建議，以確保動物福利為目的。新法案已經完成草擬階段，有望在明年初正式立法。如果順利獲得通過，德國各州狗主都必須遵守。"},{"pid":"526b1596cb263b2f57c7ce6b2b3e1691268401aa","tid":2167378,"uid":331590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:34:22.000Z","msg":"幾時到中國呀"},{"pid":"f932eff7affa37da551782e6b6e2235d4c2a06a0","tid":2167378,"uid":162268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"526b1596cb263b2f57c7ce6b2b3e1691268401aa","tid":2167378,"uid":331590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:34:22